data.description: This remodeled home is located across the street from Swartswood Lake State Park. It offers 3 bedrooms and 2 full baths with a large finished lower level. The upper level has an open floor plan with a brand new eat-in kitchen and hardwood floors throughout. The living room has large windows and a lovely fireplace for you to enjoy. The dining room is located by the deck which could be accessed through the slider doors. The kitchen has must see new cabinets, new appliances, and added recess lighting. Both bathrooms are located on the upper level. The lower level includes a spacious room with access to the patio. You can also access the two car garage through the lower level. For your convenience, the washer and dryer, along with the utilities are located on the lower level. Since the woods located in the back of the property is state owned, it provides additional privacy to the homeowners. It's also moments away from local amenities, schools, parks, & highways. Don't miss this incredible opportunity to own a renovated, move-in ready home in Newton, NJ. Experience the essence of modern comfort & elegance!
